Class SqlParser

java.lang.Object
com.trophonius.sql.SqlParser
public class SqlParser
extends java.lang.Object
Main SQL Parser Class. Contains non-SQL methods, like show databases, and dispatches SQL to parsers for DML, DDL or DCL
